6] -&gt; EXT5EXT5 -&gt; Aout2 -&gt; B(B&gt;&gt;A -&gt; ans)ans -&gt; in</code></pre><h3 id="13-SRA">13.SRA</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/zzhaire/markdown_imgs/raw/master/img/20230903153504.png" alt="image-20230903153503190"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/zzhaire/markdown_imgs/raw/master/img/20230903153512.png" alt="image-20230903153511161"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/zzhaire/markdown_imgs/raw/master/img/20230903153521.png" alt="image-20230903153519996"></p><pre><code>PC -&gt; IMEMPC + 4 -&gt; NPCNPC -&gt; PCIMEM[10:6] -&gt; EXT5EXT5 -&gt; Aout2 -&gt; B(B&gt;&gt;A -&gt; ans)ans -&gt; in</code></pre><h2 id="通路类型4">通路类型4</h2><h3 id="14-SLLV">14.SLLV</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/zzhaire/markdown_imgs/raw/master/img/20230903153556.png" alt="image-20230903153555626"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/zzhaire/markdown_imgs/raw/master/img/20230903153603.png" alt="image-20230903153602037"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/zzhaire/markdown_imgs/raw/master/img/20230903153615.png" alt="image-20230903153614340"></p><pre><code>PC -&gt; IMEMPC + 4 -&gt; NPCNPC -&gt; PCout1[4:0] -&gt; EXT5EXT5 -&gt; Aout2 -&gt; B(A&lt;&lt;B -&gt; ans)ans -&gt; in</code></pre><h3 id="15-SRLV">15.SRLV</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/zzhaire/markdown_imgs/raw/master/img/20230903153637.png" alt="image-20230903153636747"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/zzhaire/markdown_imgs/raw/master/img/20230903153649.png" alt="image-20230903153648629"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/zzhaire/markdown_imgs/raw/master/img/20230903153659.png" alt="image-20230903153657786"></p><pre><code>PC -&gt; IMEMPC + 4 -&gt; NPCNPC -&gt; PCout1[4:0] -&gt; EXT5EXT5 -&gt; Aout2 -&gt; B(A &gt;&gt; B -&gt; ans)ans -&gt; in</code></pre><h3 id="16-SRAV">16.SRAV</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/zzhaire/markdown_imgs/raw/master/img/20230903153722.png" alt="image-20230903153721162"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/zzhaire/markdown_imgs/raw/master/img/20230903153728.png" alt="image-20230903153727591"></p><p>